OL,3,CRegulator Ofcom urges tech firms to
OL,4,C'step up' to protect women and girls
OL,5,Conline
OL,7,FThe regulator has now set out guidance
OL,8,Ffor a range of providers including
OL,9,Fsocial media platforms, dating, gaming
OL,10,Fand pornography sites, urging them to
OL,11,Ftake more responsibility for
OL,12,Fprotecting users online.
OL,14,FIn an open letter to providers,
OL,15,FOfcom's chief executive Dame Melanie
OL,16,FDawes warned the digital world is "not
OL,17,Fserving women and girls the way it
OL,18,Fshould."
OL,26,@xD@cOUzD@HO]
