OL,3,CRegulator Ofcom urges tech firms to
OL,4,C'step up' to protect women and girls
OL,5,Conline
OL,7,FShe added: "In fact, it is actively
OL,8,Fharming their participation and even
OL,9,Ffacilitating abuse. Women in sport, in
OL,10,Fpolitics or in any part of public life
OL,11,Fface significant and widespread abuse
OL,12,Fonline every day."
OL,14,FSetting out their guidance to firms,
OL,15,Fshe said there is "an urgent need for
OL,16,Findustry-wide action".
