OL,4,C'step up' to protect women and girls
OL,5,Conline
OL,7,FOfcom has said it will publish a
OL,8,Freport in summer 2027, setting out the
OL,9,Fprogress companies have made.
OL,11,FBut it added: "If their action falls
OL,12,Fshort, we will consider making formal
OL,13,Frecommendations to government on where
OL,14,Fthe Online Safety Act may need to be
OL,15,Fstrengthened."
